'''VoLTE'''（'''Voice over Long-Term Evolution'''或'''Voice over LTE'''，一般稱'''高清通话'''，又譯為'''长期演进语音承载'''）是一个面向[[手机|手机]]和数据终端的高速[[无线通信|无线通信]]标准。它基于[[IP多媒体子系统|IP多媒体子系统]]（IMS）网络，在[[長期演進技術|LTE]]上使用为[[控制层面|控制层面]]（Control plane）和语音服务的[[媒体层面|媒体层面]]（Media plane）特制的配置文件（由[[GSM協會|GSM協會]]在PRD IR.92中定义）<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gsma.com/newsroom/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/IR.92-v7.0.pdf|title=Official Document IR.92 – IMS Profile for Voice and SMS|accessdate=14 September 2014|author=Nick Russell|date=3 March 2013|format=PDF|publisher=GSMA|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224162043/https://www.gsma.com/newsroom/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/IR.92-v7.0.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，这使语音服务（控制和媒体层面）作为数据流在LTE数据承载网络中传输，而不再需维护和依赖传统的[[电路交换|电路交换]]语音网络。VoLTE的语音和数据容量超过3G UMTS三倍以上，超过2G GSM六倍以上。因为VoLTE数据包[[信头|信头]]比未优化的VoIP/LTE更小，它也更有效地利用了[[带宽|带宽]]。<ref name="elkin">{{Cite news|url=http://blog.tmcnet.com/next-generation-communications/2014/04/the-secret-value-of-volte.html|title=The Secret Value of VoLTE|last=Elkin|first=Ed|date=10 April 2014|work=TMCnet|accessdate=14 September 2014|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006074657/http://blog.tmcnet.com/next-generation-communications/2014/04/the-secret-value-of-volte.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
2014年5月，[[新加坡电信|新加坡电信]]宣布世界首个商用“全功能”VoLTE服务落地[[新加坡|新加坡]]，仅可搭配[[三星Galaxy_Note_3|三星Galaxy Note 3]]使用，之后扩展到[[三星Galaxy_S6|三星Galaxy S6]]系列、[[iPhone_6s|iPhone 6s]]、[[LG_G4|LG G4]]和[[Sony_Xperia_Z3+|Sony Xperia Z3+]]、Sony Xperia Z5 Premium。<ref name="VoLTE Asia">{{Cite web|url=http://info.singtel.com/about-us/news-releases/singtel-samsung-and-ericsson-unveil-worlds-first-full-featured-voice-over-lte|title=SingTel, Samsung and Ericsson unveil world's first full-featured Voice over LTE service|accessdate=4 August 2014|date=19 May 2014|publisher=SingTel|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808071230/http://info.singtel.com/about-us/news-releases/singtel-samsung-and-ericsson-unveil-worlds-first-full-featured-voice-over-lte|archive-date=2014-08-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2014年6月，[[韩国电信|韩国电信]]展示了世界首个基于VoLTE的[[漫遊|漫遊]]服务。[[韩国|韩国]]{{tsl|en|Mobile network operator|运营商}}、[[中国移动|中国移动]]及[[csl.|csl.]]合作开发VoLTE漫游服务。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.telegeography.com/products/commsupdate/articles/2014/06/13/kt-and-china-mobile-claim-world-first-for-cross-border-volte-roaming/?utm_source=CommsUpdate&utm_campaign=d5a730874d-CommsUpdate+13+June+2014&utm_medium=email&utm_term=0_0688983330-d5a730874d-8809561|title=KT and China Mobile claim world first for cross-border VoLTE roaming|accessdate=14 September 2014|date=13 June 2014|publisher=TeleGeography|archive-date=2018-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181114224119/https://www.telegeography.com/products/commsupdate/articles/2014/06/13/kt-and-china-mobile-claim-world-first-for-cross-border-volte-roaming/?utm_source=CommsUpdate&utm_campaign=d5a730874d-CommsUpdate+13+June+2014&utm_medium=email&utm_term=0_0688983330-d5a730874d-8809561|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年10月，运营商使用家庭路由系统基于IMS本地breakout架构。{{what}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.telecompaper.com/news/china-kpn-ibasis-implement-first-volte-roaming-calls--1042834|title=China, KPN, iBasis implement first VoLTE roaming calls|accessdate=2014-10-14|date=2014-10-14|publisher=Telecompaper|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030174240/https://www.telecompaper.com/news/china-kpn-ibasis-implement-first-volte-roaming-calls--1042834|dead-url=no}}</ref>

